    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in truly pristine, showroom condition\u2014honestly, you'd think it just rolled off the lot! It\u2019s been babied since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and drives like an absolute dream. I\u2019m really sad to see it go, but I\u2019m looking for a new owner who will appreciate it as much as I have. You\u2019ve got to see it in person to believe how perfect it is! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look.",
      "price": 44500.0,
