    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2008 BMW M3 (E92) Coupe, a superlative example of the final naturally aspirated M-car. At its heart lies the S65 4.0L V8, utilizing eight individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double-VANOS system to achieve an 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen features a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox paired with the M Variable Differential Lock for optimal longitudinal and lateral traction. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing an uncompromising balance between compliance and track-ready stiffness. Mechanically flawless, this M3 has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. The Alpine White paint and Novillo leather interior remain in concours-level condition, reflecting a life of climate-controlled storage and meticulous stewardship.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Excellent condition. Garage kept. No accidents. Original paint. Full service records included.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since its original purchase. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero imperfections, scratches, or stone chips. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and scent-free, with every electronic component and convenience feature functioning exactly as it did the day it left the factory. This is a single-owner vehicle with a documented, comprehensive service history performed exclusively at authorized dealerships. The engine bay is spotless, the tires are near-new, and the undercarriage shows no signs of wear or weather exposure. This is not just a used car; it is a collector-grade investment for the discerning driver who demands perfection. Viewing is highly recommended to appreciate the flawless state of this machine.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 36
    },
    {
